<p>
@HI{{@EM{{semete}}}} is an adverb that indicates the speaker's minimally satisfactory level.
It expresses the idea of "at least". The speaker is aware that it is not possible to realise an ideal state and so indicates an acceptable level instead.
The sentence should end in a direct or indirect expression of desire.

